Exercise: Write a void function to draw a star, where the length of each side is 100 units.
(Hint: You should turn the turtle by 144 degrees at each point.)
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Solution: 

import turtle

def turtle_window():
        turtle.Screen()
        turtle.Turtle()

def star(length, angle):
    for i in range(5):
        turtle.forward(length)
        turtle.left(angle)

star(100, 144)

